                The ThreadSpecificationId element is the QIF id of the
                thread specification for the thread characteristic. This
                shall be the QIF id of a thread specification.
              </xs:documentation>
            </xs:annotation>
          </xs:element>
        </xs:sequence>
      </xs:extension>
    </xs:complexContent>
